<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-2377] sub-tabbedPane in swingbuilder missing title</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2377</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I found that the sub-tabbedPane can not have a title, the test code is shown as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; groovy.swing.*

def swing = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; SwingBuilder()
def frame = swing.frame() {

    tabbedPane() {
        label(text:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;a&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, title:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;ta&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
        tabbedPane() {
            label(text:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;sa&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, title:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;sta&apos;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// the title named sta does not show :(
&lt;/span&gt;            label(text:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;sb&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, title:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;stb&apos;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// the title named stb does not show, too :(
&lt;/span&gt;        }
    }
}

frame.pack()
frame.show()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
